gulation, loss and theft of data, incorrect data, and overfitting.\"", "\"USES OF BIG DATA AND DATA ANALYTICS\":\"Big data and data analytics are used by companies like Netflix, Amazon, British Airways, and Target to predict customer preferences, personalize marketing, plan routes, and offer targeted discounts.\"", "\"IMPORTANCE OF DATA VISUALISATION\":\"Data visualisation is the display of information graphically, using various forms such as charts, graphs, and maps. It aims to present data in a form that is easy to understand and analyse, summarising big data in a way that even non-technical users may understand.\"", "\"MARKETING INSIGHTS\":\"Analytical findings can provide marketing insights to enhance decision-making and performance management.\"", "\"CUSTOMER SERVICE IMPROVEMENTS\":\"Analytical findings can provide customer service improvements to enhance decision-making and performance management.\"", "\"COMPETITIVE STRENGTH\":\"Analytical findings can provide competitive strength to enhance decision-making and performance management.\"", "\"CUSTOMER LOYALTY\":\"Analytical findings can provide customer loyalty to enhance decision-making and performance management.\"", "\"OPERATIONAL EFFICIENCY\":\"OPERATIONAL EFFICIENCY\" is the ability to deliver products or services in the most cost-effective manner without compromising quality. It is a key factor in achieving profitability and sustainability. Analytical findings can provide operational efficiency to enhance decision-making and performance management.", "\"PERFORMANCE MEASUREMENT\":\"Performance Measurement\" is the process of evaluating how effectively an organization achieves its objectives, using both financial and non-financial performance indicators. It involves assessing the efficiency and effectiveness of a production system through various metrics and indicators. Performance measurement shows how well an organization achieves its stated objectives, ranking these objectives from the mission level to lower-level goals. Analytical findings derived from performance measurement can enhance decision-making and performance management.", "\"COST\":\"Potential dangers and drawbacks of using big data include cost.\"", "\"TIME AND STAFF RESOURCES\":\"Potential dangers and drawbacks of using big data include time and staff resources.\"", "\"REGULATION\":\"Potential dangers and drawbacks of using big data include regulation.\"", "\"LOSS AND THEFT OF DATA\":\"Potential dangers and drawbacks of using big data include loss and theft of data.\""], "parameters": {"model": "text-embedding-3-small", "temperature": 0.0, "frequency_penalty": null, "presence_penalty": null, "top_p": 1.0, "max_tokens": 4000, "n": 1}}